<body>

<h1>KaviCakes Technical Development & Quality Assurance Report</h1>

<p><strong>Prepared for:</strong> Technical Review Board</p>
<p><strong>Date:</strong> April 16, 2026</p>

<hr>

<h2>1. Technologies & Tools Overview</h2>
<p>The KaviCakes system is built using a modern Full-Stack Architecture designed for high performance, scalability, and security.</p>

<h3>Core Implementation Technologies:</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Frontend (Client-Side):</strong> React.js (v18+) using Functional Components and Hooks.</li>
    <li><strong>Backend (Server-Side):</strong> Node.js with Express.js framework for RESTful API management.</li>
    <li><strong>Database:</strong> MySQL relational database managed via Prisma ORM for type-safe queries.</li>
    <li><strong>CSS Frameworks:</strong> Tailwind CSS (for Customer Site aesthetic) and Ant Design (for Admin Panel efficiency).</li>
    <li><strong>State Management:</strong> React Context API for Global Auth and Cart state.</li>
</ul>

<hr>

